11:06.265 --> 11:09.868
How about you?
How many?

11:09.870 --> 11:11.236
- Thousands.

11:14.874 --> 11:16.374
- Are they both dead?

11:16.376 --> 11:17.442
- No.

11:17.444 --> 11:19.344
