11:31.124 --> 11:33.158
- Man, that's the worst.

11:33.160 --> 11:35.894
- No, it's not the worst.

11:35.896 --> 11:37.729
But it's not great.

11:37.731 --> 11:39.030
- And your mom--
where's she?

11:39.032 --> 11:40.965
- [sighs]
I never really know.

11:40.967 --> 11:43.034
