14:17.991 --> 14:19.591
- Do you consider yourself

14:19.593 --> 14:21.159
A good person?

14:21.161 --> 14:23.061
- No.

14:23.063 --> 14:24.963
- No?
- No.

14:24.965 --> 14:28.566
